title: 18th Anniversary | Attendance Figures
body_text:
... Pham, Vicki, and their daughter Mia were there. Robert Brown was there. Valerie was there.
My mom, step-dad, two aunts, two cousins, two second cousins, and my fav guy Anthony were all there.
THIS ONE was special.
